This project is built using Django and Django REST Framework.
The purpose of this assignment is to create a REST API that manages User profiles using /api/users/ endpoints.

The API allows performing full CRUD operations:

1. Create a user
2. Read (list) users
3. Retrieve a single user
4. Update a user
5. Delete a user


Technology Used

1. Python
2. Django
3. Django REST Framework
4. QLite (default database)

